 ciel","en":"(rain from) the sky","tr":"l-samāa","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"عَلَيْكُم","fr":"sur vous","en":"upon you","tr":"ʿalaykum","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"مِّدْرَارًۭا","fr":"(dans) abondance","en":"(in) abundance","tr":"mid'rāran","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":12,"verseKey":"71:12","juz":29,"arabic":"وَيُمْدِدْكُم بِأَمْوَٰلٍ وَبَنِينَ وَيَجْعَل لَّكُمْ جَنَّـٰتٍ وَيَجْعَل لَّكُمْ أَنْهَـٰرًا","fr":"vous dispensera avec largesse beaucoup de richesses et d’enfants, et vous accordera des jardins et vous accordera des rivières.","en":"And give you increase in wealth and children and provide for you gardens and provide for you rivers.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَيُمْدِدْكُم","fr":"Et pourvoir vous","en":"And provide you","tr":"wayum'did'kum","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"بِأَمْوَٰلٍۢ","fr":"avec richesse","en":"with wealth","tr":"bi-amwālin","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"وَبَنِينَ","fr":"et enfants","en":"and children","tr":"wabanīna","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"وَيَجْعَل","fr":"et faire","en":"and make","tr":"wayajʿal","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"لَّكُمْ","fr":"pour vous","en":"for you","tr":"lakum","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"جَنَّـٰتٍۢ","fr":"jardins","en":"gardens","tr":"jannātin","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"وَيَجْعَل","fr":"et faire","en":"and make","tr":"wayajʿal","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"لَّكُمْ","fr":"pour vous","en":"for you","tr":"lakum","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"أَنْهَـٰرًۭا","fr":"rivières","en":"rivers","tr":"anhāran","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":13,"verseKey":"71:13","juz":29,"arabic":"مَّا لَكُمْ لَا تَرْجُونَ لِلَّهِ وَقَارًا","fr":"Pourquoi donc ne témoignez-vous à Allah aucune vénération digne de ce nom ?","en":"What is [the matter] with you that you do not attribute to Allāh [due] grandeur","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"مَّا","fr":"Quoi","en":"What","tr":"mā","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"لَكُمْ","fr":"(est) pour vous","en":"(is) for you","tr":"lakum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"لَا","fr":"non","en":"not","tr":"lā","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"تَرْجُونَ","fr":"vous attribuez","en":"you attribute","tr":"tarjūna","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"لِلَّهِ","fr":"à Allah","en":"to Allah","tr":"lillahi","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"وَقَارًۭا","fr":"grandeur","en":"grandeur","tr":"waqāran","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":14,"verseKey":"71:14","juz":29,"arabic":"وَقَدْ خَلَقَكُمْ أَطْوَارًا","fr":"C’est bien Lui Qui vous a pourtant créés par étapes !","en":"While He has created you in stages?","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَقَدْ","fr":"Et certes","en":"And indeed","tr":"waqad","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"خَلَقَكُمْ","fr":"Il vous a créés","en":"He created you","tr":"khalaqakum","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"أَطْوَارًا","fr":"(dans) étapes","en":"(in) stages","tr":"aṭwāran","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":15,"verseKey":"71:15","juz":29,"arabic":"أَلَمْ تَرَوْا۟ كَيْفَ خَلَقَ ٱللَّهُ سَبْعَ سَمَـٰوَٰتٍ طِبَاقًا","fr":"Ne voyez-vous pas comment Allah a créé sept cieux qui se superposent,","en":"Do you not consider how Allāh has created seven heavens in layers","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"أَلَمْ","fr":"Ne fais pas","en":"Do not","tr":"alam","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"تَرَوْا۟","fr":"vous voyez","en":"you see","tr":"taraw","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"كَيْفَ","fr":"comment","en":"how","tr":"kayfa","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"خَلَقَ","fr":"fit créer","en":"did create","tr":"khalaqa","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"ٱللَّهُ","fr":"Allah","en":"Allah","tr":"l-lahu","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"سَبْعَ","fr":"(le) sept","en":"(the) seven","tr":"sabʿa","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"سَمَـٰوَٰتٍۢ","fr":"cieux","en":"heavens","tr":"samāwātin","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"طِبَاقًۭا","fr":"(dans) couches","en":"(in) layers","tr":"ṭibāqan","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":16,"verseKey":"71:16","juz":29,"arabic":"وَجَعَلَ ٱلْقَمَرَ فِيهِنَّ نُورًا وَجَعَلَ ٱلشَّمْسَ سِرَاجًا","fr